    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost">He</supplied>rcul<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">T</supplied>ert&amp;lt;i&amp;gt;nius <lb n="3"/>Catulli<lb break="no" n="4"/>nus <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>ivitatis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>in <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei aneinanderpassende Fragmente erhalten. Z. 2: zwischen T und N möglicherwise ein kleines I erkennbar. (B): Schmidt: Z. 1: [T]ertinius; Mattern: Z. 4: de(curio); Schmidt; Mattern: Z. 5: i[n].</p>
            </div>
